<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="tend-vi">tend <strong><em>vi</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /tend/    美 /tend/  </p>
<p>[用于以下惯用语]</p>
<h2 id="_1">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="tend-to-towards-sth">tend to / toward(s) sth</h3>
<p>1.★ <strong>倾向于；有...的趋势：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The sort of music I listen to varies, but it tends toward light music.
我所听的音乐形形色色，不过一般都是轻音乐。</p></div>

<h3 id="tend-to-do-sth">tend to do sth</h3>
<p>1.★ <strong>易于做某事；往往会做某事</strong><br />
to usually do or be sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I tend to see pictures in my mind when I am reading or listening.
在读或者听的时候，我往往会在头脑中形成图像。</p><footer>人教⑩ – 4</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Readers tended to share articles that were exciting or funny.
读者往往分享那些令人兴奋或者有趣的文章。</p><footer>2016 全国</footer></div></div>